{"tid":1427094,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎！！！另類民居戰場需要你！！！","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:31:07.000Z","uid":272538,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"663f7b05886a975a019e283440a3f5f2659f99f0","tid":1427094,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"適合：<br />\n- 晚上不方便外出<br />\n- 想付出但真係去唔到前線<br />\n嘅你地！！！<br />\n<br />\n首選戰區：<br />\n- 深水埗<br />\n- 黃大仙<br />\n<br />\n次選：<br />\n- 上環<br />\n- 西環<br />\n- 機場<br />\n<br />\n要做乜：<br />\n- 派發N95口罩+細支裝生理鹽水<br />\n- 解釋一下可以有啲乜嘢後遺症<br />\n- 可以派下文宣<br />\n<br />\n點解：<br />\n因為大量嘅居民就算係經過或者住喺附近，其實都受到催淚彈嘅刺激，好多亦話寵物亦受影響，係咁流眼水同埋不適<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點：<br />\n1. 令居民知道<span style=\"color: red;\">只有我哋</span>關心佢地嘅身體健唔健康 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府唔在乎！警察唔理！</span><br />\n2. 令佢哋知道其實前線受左幾大嘅風險</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外表要求：<br />\n企理大方整潔<br />\n甚至越靚越好，面帶微笑<br />\n親切有禮<br />\n唔好令街坊一見到我哋就覺得我地搞事<br />\n<br />\n請報名<br />\n<br />\n另外如有認識經銷商或藥廠<br />\n或有購買大量用品經驗的<br />\n請留聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe5eebadfec0bdf87c04014022c17af9750793b","tid":1427094,"uid":20908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"街坊戰線<br />\n人人有責呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2541a15098275409e132c17f812598c5e06ce74","tid":1427094,"uid":223972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:58:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73c8efbf4ecea664a2f941474b331e6201c741ed","tid":1427094,"uid":272538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"如果